🛠️ Setup Instructions
1. Prerequisites
XAMPP (or any local server with PHP 8.0+ and MySQL).

A browser (Chrome/Edge recommended).

2. Database Installation
Open phpMyAdmin (http://localhost/phpmyadmin).

Create a new database named tech_store.

Click the Import tab.

Choose the provided tech_store.sql file and click Go.

3. Files Setup
Move the phone-store folder into your XAMPP htdocs directory (usually C:\xampp\htdocs\).

Ensure the uploads/ folder exists and has write permissions.

Open your browser and navigate to http://localhost/phone-store/index.php.
